    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i get that it can be both, but it feels like people usually only talk about the bad stuff. can't you just have a healthy sense of national pride without it becoming toxic? it seems like you're kind of leaning towards the idea that nationalism is inherently a problem that just needs to be managed.",
